snippet.title: Singer Neha Kakkar interview with Farhan Kazi | Nagpur Today
Neha Kakkar recorded 'Manali Trance' 20 mins | Exclusive Interview
snippet.description:
Bollywood singer Neha Kakkar in conversation with Mr. Komal Nahta about  her experience of working in the Hindi film industry so far. Neha's voice has  been heard in songs like 'Aao Raja', 'Second Hand Jawaani' and the very popular  'Manali Trance'. Neha also reveals how she has begun the 'selfie video' concept  and the same has been launched officially with 'Gabbar Is Back'. Neha Kakkar is  very popular with her fans and is 3 Million fans strong on Facebook. Neha  Kakkar is the voice behind 'London Thumakda' from award-winning film, 'Queen'  as well. She has worked with music directors like Yo Yo Honey Singh, Sachin- Jigar, Pritam and many more and looks forward to singing many more songs.

snippet.title: Neha Kakkar on all her firsts | S01E06 | Pinkvilla | Bollywood
snippet.description:
Neha Kakkar recently met with Pinkvilla and revealed to us all her firsts. From her first ever job, to her first mata ki chowki, to her first ever co-star to her first day in Mumbai. The singer gave us insights and also narrated her experiences and incidents. Watch on the video to know all of Neha Kakkar's firsts. 

Neha Kakkar is an Indian singer and performer who participated in the singing reality show Indian Idol 2. Since then there has been no looking back for the curly haired beauty. Neha has also appeared in Comedy Circus Ke Taansen in 2014 and was also a judge on Sa Re Ga Ma Pa Lil Champs.

snippet.title: Space Out With Neha Kakkar | From Being The Contestant To The Judge of Indian Idol | Interview
snippet.description:
Neha Kakkar was just 17 years old when she made it to the second season of singing reality show Indian Idol. As destiny would have it,  she is back again as the judge of Indian Idol season 10. From being an aam admi to the most followed Indian celebrity on Instagram, the journey has been no short of a magic for her. Hear her tale, as Badsha caught up with the singing Diva in the latest episode of Space Out.
